'''理查德·布瑞克'''（{{lang-en|Richard Michael Brick}}，{{bd|1945年|9月20日|2014年|4月2日|catIdx=Brick}}），是一名美国电影制片人<ref name="imdb">{{Citation | title = Internet Movie Database: Richard Brick | url = http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0003673/ | accessdate = August 5, 2009 | archive-date = 2017-02-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170216155709/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0003673/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>，美国[[哥伦比亚大学|哥伦比亚大学]]教授<ref name="columbia">{{Citation | title = Columbia University School of the Arts Film Division Faculty | url = http://wwwapp.cc.columbia.edu/art/app/arts/film/faculty-bio.jsp?faculty=19 | accessdate = August 5, 2009 }}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref name="nytimes">{{Citation | title = Dinkins Turns to Industry Experience to Lure Films Back to City | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1992/11/25/nyregion/dinkins-turns-to-industry-experience-to-lure-films-back-to-city.html | date = November 25, 1992 | author = Janofsky, Michael | journal = The New York Times | accessdate = August 5, 2009 | archive-date = 2018-01-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180116052910/http://www.nytimes.com/1992/11/25/nyregion/dinkins-turns-to-industry-experience-to-lure-films-back-to-city.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2014年，他因[[食管癌|食管癌]]去世，享年68岁<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/04/06/arts/richard-brick-who-drew-films-back-to-new-york-dies-at-68.html?_r=0|title=Richard Brick, Who Drew Films Back to New York, Dies at 68|publisher=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]].com|accessdate=April 2, 2014|archive-date=2020-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808101145/https://www.nytimes.com/2014/04/06/arts/richard-brick-who-drew-films-back-to-new-york-dies-at-68.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

